<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({"@context":"https://schema.org","@graph":[{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://stackarchitect.xyz/faq/what-is-google-enhanced-conversions#webpage","url":"https://stackarchitect.xyz/faq/what-is-google-enhanced-conversions/","name":"What Is Google Enhanced Conversions? — Shopify Guide 2026 | Stack Architect","description":"Google Enhanced Conversions supplements browser-based Google Ads tracking by sending hashed first-party customer data server-side — recovering conversions lost to iOS restrictions and Safari ITP. Free for Shopify via Make.com in 6 minutes.","datePublished":"2026-04-21","dateModified":"2026-04-21","inLanguage":"en-GB","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://stackarchitect.xyz/#website"},"speakable":{"@type":"SpeakableSpecification","cssSelector":[".quick-answer p","h1"]}},{"@type":"BreadcrumbList","itemListElement":[{"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"name":"Home","item":"https://stackarchitect.xyz/"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":2,"name":"FAQ","item":"https://stackarchitect.xyz/faq/"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":3,"name":"What Is Google Enhanced Conversions?","item":"https://stackarchitect.xyz/faq/what-is-google-enhanced-conversions/"}]},{"@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"What is Google Enhanced Conversions?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Google Enhanced Conversions is a Google Ads feature that supplements standard browser-based conversion tracking by sending hashed first-party customer data — email address and phone number, encrypted with SHA-256 — directly to Google via server-side API. Google uses this data to match purchases to signed-in Google accounts, recovering conversion credit that was lost because the standard gTag was blocked by iOS, Safari ITP, or ad blockers. Enhanced Conversions improves Smart Bidding and Performance Max optimisation accuracy."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What is the difference between Google Enhanced Conversions and standard Google Ads tracking?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Standard Google Ads conversion tracking fires a browser-based gTag script on the thank-you page after checkout. It can be blocked by iOS Link Tracking Protection, Safari ITP clearing the gclid cookie, or ad blockers preventing the script from loading. Google Enhanced Conversions sends hashed customer data (email, phone) server-to-server independently of the browser — Google matches this data to signed-in Google accounts even when the gTag fails. Running both simultaneously gives Google the most accurate conversion picture."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How does Google Enhanced Conversions help Shopify stores?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"For Shopify stores, Google Enhanced Conversions recovers purchase attribution that was lost due to iOS privacy restrictions and Safari Intelligent Tracking Prevention. iOS 17+ strips the gclid parameter from ad URLs, making it impossible for the browser-based gTag to attribute purchases to Google Ads clicks. Enhanced Conversions supplements this by matching the Shopify order email to the Google account that clicked the ad — recovering attribution even without gclid. Most Shopify stores recover 15–35% more attributed conversions."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Google Enhanced Conversions free for Shopify?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Google Enhanced Conversions API is free to use. The Stack Architect implementation via Make.com is also free — it uses Make.com\'s free tier to send hashed customer data server-side to the Google Ads Conversions API. The complete setup takes 6 minutes and costs $0/month ongoing."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How is Google Enhanced Conversions different from Meta CAPI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Google Enhanced Conversions and Meta Conversions API (CAPI) solve the same fundamental problem — recovering conversion data lost to iOS and browser-based tracking failures — but for different ad platforms. Google Enhanced Conversions routes data to Google Ads for Smart Bidding and Performance Max optimisation. Meta CAPI routes data to Meta for Advantage+ Shopping and Manual campaign attribution. Both use hashed customer data. Both can be set up free via Make.com and run simultaneously from the same Shopify webhook."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What data does Google Enhanced Conversions send to Google?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Google Enhanced Conversions sends SHA-256 hashed versions of the customer\'s email address, phone number, first name, last name, and shipping address. Raw personal data is never transmitted — only the irreversible hash. Google uses this hash to look up whether a signed-in Google account matches the customer who purchased, then assigns conversion credit to the ad click that brought them. This process is GDPR-compliant when disclosed in your privacy policy."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Does Google Enhanced Conversions improve Smart Bidding?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Smart Bidding, Target ROAS, and Performance Max all optimise based on the conversion signals Google receives. When 20–35% of real conversions are invisible due to iOS and browser tracking failures, the algorithm underbids on high-intent audiences and overspends on low-converting segments. Completing conversion data with Enhanced Conversions typically improves Smart Bidding performance within 14–21 days as the model incorporates the additional conversion history."}}]}]})}/>
<style is:global>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}html{scroll-behavior:smooth}body{background:#080c0a;color:#f1f5f9;font-family:'Inter',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}
:root{--bg:#080c0a;--bg-2:#0c110f;--bg-3:#111916;--g:#00c864;--g-dim:rgba(0,200,100,.07);--g-b:rgba(0,200,100,.2);--sky:#38bdf8;--sky-dim:rgba(56,189,248,.07);--vio:#c4b5fd;--vio-dim:rgba(196,181,253,.07);--amber:#f59e0b;--red:#ef4444;--tiktok:#ff2d55;--border:rgba(255,255,255,.07);--text:#f1f5f9;--text-2:#cbd5e1;--text-3:#94a3b8;--text-4:#64748b;--mono:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;--sans:'Inter',-apple-system,sans-serif;--r:8px}
@keyframes dotPing{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.3}}@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(0,200,100,.4)}70%{box-shadow:0 0 0 8px rgba(0,200,100,0)}}
/* NAV */
.product-terminal-bar{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:1000;background:rgba(8,12,10,.96);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:0 24px}
.product-terminal-bar.scrolled{border-bottom-color:rgba(0,200,100,.18)}
.terminal-container{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;height:56px}
.terminal-status{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-4);letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;white-space:nowrap;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px}
.status-indicator{display:inline-block;width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--g);animation:dotPing 2.2s ease-in-out infinite}
.product-access-grid{list-style:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:2px;flex:1;overflow:hidden}
.product-link{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-3);padding:6px 9px;border-radius:4px;transition:color .15s,background .15s;white-space:nowrap}
.product-link:hover,.product-link.is-active{color:var(--g);background:var(--g-dim)}.home-node{color:var(--text-4)}
.dropdown{position:relative}
.dropdown-menu{display:none;position:absolute;top:calc(100% + 8px);left:0;background:#0d1410;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;min-width:260px;padding:6px;flex-direction:column;gap:2px;z-index:100;box-shadow:0 16px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.7)}
.dropdown:hover .dropdown-menu{display:flex}
.dropdown-menu a{padding:8px 12px;border-radius:4px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-3)}
.dropdown-menu a:hover{background:var(--g-dim);color:var(--g)}
.dropdown-desc{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:11px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0;text-transform:none;color:var(--text-4);line-height:1.4}
.terminal-cta{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-left:auto;flex-shrink:0}
.savings-ticker{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--g);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.12em;white-space:nowrap}
.cta-node{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;background:var(--g);color:#020617;padding:8px 14px;border-radius:4px;white-space:nowrap;transition:opacity .15s}
.cta-node:hover{opacity:.88}
/* TAGS */
.tag{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:3px;border:1px solid var(--g-b);color:var(--g);background:var(--g-dim)}
.tag-dim{border-color:var(--border);color:var(--text-4);background:transparent}
.tag-sky{border-color:rgba(56,189,248,.25);color:var(--sky);background:var(--sky-dim)}
.tag-vio{border-color:rgba(196,181,253,.2);color:var(--vio);background:var(--vio-dim)}
.tag-amber{border-color:rgba(245,158,11,.25);color:var(--amber);background:rgba(245,158,11,.06)}
.tag-tiktok{border-color:rgba(255,45,85,.25);color:var(--tiktok);background:rgba(255,45,85,.06)}
/* BTNS */
.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:14px;font-weight:700;padding:13px 26px;border-radius:var(--r);background:var(--g);color:#020617;transition:opacity .2s,transform .2s;text-decoration:none;border:none;cursor:pointer}
.btn:hover{opacity:.88;transform:translateY(-1px)}.btn.pulse{animation:pulse 2.5s ease-in-out infinite}
.btn-outline{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:14px;font-weight:700;padding:13px 26px;border-radius:var(--r);border:1.5px solid var(--g-b);color:var(--g);background:transparent;transition:background .2s;text-decoration:none}
.btn-outline:hover{background:var(--g-dim)}.btn-sm{padding:10px 20px;font-size:13px}.btn-outline-sm{padding:10px 20px;font-size:13px}
/* LAYOUT */
.section{padding:72px 24px;background:var(--bg)}.section-alt{padding:72px 24px;background:var(--bg-3)}
.inner{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto}.inner-md{max-width:860px;margin:0 auto}.inner-sm{max-width:760px;margin:0 auto}
.sec-head{text-align:center;margin-bottom:40px}
.sec-head h2{font-family:var(--sans);font-weight:900;font-size:clamp(22px,3.5vw,34px);letter-spacing:-.03em;color:var(--text);line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:10px}
.sec-head p{font-size:15px;color:var(--text-3);max-width:500px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.75}
.dot{display:inline-block;width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--g);animation:dotPing 2.2s ease-in-out infinite}
/* HERO / ANSWER */
.faq-hero{padding:40px 24px 56px;background:var(--bg)}
.faq-hero-inner{max-width:860px;margin:0 auto}
.hero-dateline{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.15em;color:var(--text-4);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:18px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.faq-hero h1{font-family:var(--sans);font-weight:900;font-size:clamp(26px,4.5vw,48px);letter-spacing:-.03em;color:var(--text);line-height:1.06;margin-bottom:28px}
.quick-answer{border-left:3px solid var(--g);padding:20px 24px;background:var(--g-dim);border-radius:0 var(--r) var(--r) 0;margin-bottom:28px}
.qa-label{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--g);margin-bottom:8px}
.quick-answer p{font-size:16px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);line-height:1.75}
.quick-answer strong{color:var(--g)}
/* STATS */
.stat-strip{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r);overflow:hidden;margin:28px 0}
.stat-cell{flex:1;min-width:110px;padding:18px 14px;text-align:center;border-right:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--bg-3)}
.stat-cell:last-child{border-right:none}
.stat-v{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:var(--g)}
.stat-l{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--text-4);letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:4px}
/* HOW-TO GRID */
.how-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r);overflow:hidden;margin:28px 0}
.how-step{padding:28px;background:var(--bg-3)}.how-step+.how-step{border-left:1px solid var(--border)}
.how-n{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.15em;color:var(--g);margin-bottom:10px}
.how-title{font-weight:800;font-size:16px;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:8px}
.how-body{font-size:14px;color:var(--text-3);line-height:1.75}
.how-tool{display:inline-block;margin-top:12px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--text-4);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:3px 8px;border-radius:3px;letter-spacing:.08em}
/* TABLES */
.compare-wrap{overflow-x:auto;margin:24px 0;border-radius:var(--r);border:1px solid var(--border)}
.compare-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13px}
.compare-table th{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-4);background:var(--bg-3);padding:13px 14px;text-align:left;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.compare-table td{padding:12px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text-3);vertical-align:middle;line-height:1.5}
.compare-table tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none}.compare-table tr:hover td{background:rgba(255,255,255,.015)}
.c-yes{color:var(--g);font-weight:700}.c-no{color:var(--red)}.c-warn{color:var(--amber)}.c-hi{background:rgba(0,200,100,.04)!important}.c-bold{font-weight:700;color:var(--text)}
/* PROSE */
.prose h2{font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(18px,2.5vw,22px);color:var(--text);letter-spacing:-.02em;margin:40px 0 12px}
.prose h3{font-weight:700;font-size:17px;color:var(--text);margin:28px 0 8px}
.prose p{font-size:15px;color:var(--text-3);line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:16px}
.prose strong{color:var(--text)}.prose a{color:var(--g);text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px}
.prose ul{margin:12px 0 16px 22px}.prose ul li{font-size:15px;color:var(--text-3);line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:6px}
.prose ol{margin:12px 0 16px 22px}.prose ol li{font-size:15px;color:var(--text-3);line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:8px}
/* CALLOUTS */
.callout{border:1px solid var(--g-b);background:var(--g-dim);border-radius:var(--r);padding:18px 22px;margin:20px 0}
.callout-label{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.15em;color:var(--g);margin-bottom:6px;text-transform:uppercase}
.callout p{font-size:14px;color:var(--text-2);margin:0;line-height:1.7}
.callout-sky{border-color:rgba(56,189,248,.25);background:var(--sky-dim)}.callout-sky .callout-label{color:var(--sky)}
.callout-amber{border-color:rgba(245,158,11,.25);background:rgba(245,158,11,.06)}.callout-amber .callout-label{color:var(--amber)}
/* KEY FACTS */
.key-facts{border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r);background:var(--bg-3);padding:24px 28px;margin:24px 0}
.key-facts-title{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-4);margin-bottom:16px}
.fact-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px}
.fact-row{display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;font-size:14px}
.fact-k{color:var(--text-4);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;min-width:130px;flex-shrink:0}
.fact-v{color:var(--text-2);font-weight:600}
/* TESTIMONIAL */
.tc{border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r);background:var(--bg-3);padding:24px;margin:0}
.tc-stars{color:var(--amber);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:.1em;margin-bottom:12px}
.tc-quote{font-size:14px;color:var(--text-3);line-height:1.8;font-style:italic;margin-bottom:14px}
.tc-name{font-weight:700;font-size:13px;color:var(--text)}
.tc-store{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--text-4);margin-top:2px;letter-spacing:.05em}
.testi-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:14px;margin-top:20px}
/* FAQ ACCORDION */
.faq-list-c{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px}
.faq-item-c{border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r);background:var(--bg-3);overflow:hidden;transition:border-color .2s}
.faq-item-c[open]{border-color:rgba(0,200,100,.25)}
.faq-item-c summary{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px;padding:18px 20px;cursor:pointer;list-style:none;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);line-height:1.5}
.faq-item-c summary::-webkit-details-marker{display:none}.faq-item-c summary:hover{color:var(--g)}
.faq-ico{flex-shrink:0;width:20px;height:20px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:50%;display:grid;place-items:center;font-size:14px;color:var(--text-4);transition:transform .25s,border-color .25s}
.faq-ico::after{content:'+'}.faq-item-c[open] .faq-ico{transform:rotate(45deg);border-color:rgba(0,200,100,.3);color:var(--g)}
.faq-ans-c{padding:0 20px 18px}.faq-ans-c p{font-size:14px;color:var(--text-3);line-height:1.8}.faq-ans-c a{color:var(--g);text-decoration:underline}
/* CTA STRIP */
.cta-strip{background:var(--bg-3);border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:36px 24px}
.cta-strip-inner{max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:24px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.cta-strip-title{font-weight:900;font-size:clamp(16px,2.5vw,20px);color:var(--text);letter-spacing:-.02em;margin-bottom:4px}
.cta-strip-sub{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-3)}.cta-strip-sub span{color:var(--g);font-weight:600}
.cta-strip-actions{display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap}
/* RELATED */
.related-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(185px,1fr));gap:12px;margin-top:20px}
.related-link{border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r);padding:16px;background:var(--bg-3);transition:border-color .2s;display:block}
.related-link:hover{border-color:rgba(0,200,100,.25)}
.related-label{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.12em;color:var(--text-4);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:6px}
.related-link h4{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-2);line-height:1.4}
/* BREADCRUMB */
.breadcrumb-wrap{padding:14px 24px 0;max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--text-4);letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase}
.breadcrumb-wrap a{color:var(--text-4);transition:color .15s}.breadcrumb-wrap a:hover{color:var(--g)}
.bc-sep{color:var(--border)}
/* FOOTER */
.architect-footer{background:var(--bg-3);border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding:56px 24px 36px}
.footer-container{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto}
.footer-conversion-strip{background:var(--g-dim);border:1px solid var(--g-b);border-radius:var(--r);padding:20px 24px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:20px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:44px}
.footer-conversion-text{font-size:14px;color:var(--text-2);font-weight:600}
.footer-conversion-text span{color:var(--text)}
.footer-conversion-cta{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;background:var(--g);color:#020617;padding:10px 18px;border-radius:4px;white-space:nowrap}
.footer-system-title{display:block;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--text-4);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:14px}
.status-bar{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;margin-bottom:28px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--text-4);letter-spacing:.12em}
.bar-sep{height:10px;width:1px;background:var(--border)}
.footer-links{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;margin-bottom:14px}
.footer-links a{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;color:var(--text-4);padding:4px 10px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:3px;transition:color .15s,border-color .15s}
.footer-links a:hover{color:var(--g);border-color:var(--g-b)}
.nav-secondary{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:14px;margin-bottom:28px}
